CreatorPilot UI Updates Complete
=================================

Date: 2026-02-06
All 7 user-requested updates have been implemented successfully.

Changes Applied:
================

1. Button Color Updates
   - Changed all white/outline buttons to purple (#9333EA) with white text
   - Updated 10+ buttons across onboarding, studio, content builder, and modals
   - Maintained ghost buttons for secondary actions (Settings)

2. View Reflection Enhancement
   - Added "This Week's Performance" section with 4 metrics:
     * Posts Published: 3
     * Total Reach: 12.4K (+24%)
     * Avg Engagement: 8.2% (+3.1%)
     * Total Saves: 156 (+18%)
   - Added summary text about posting consistency
   - Positioned between header and last session performance

3. Content Builder Insights Update
   - Replaced dynamic Pattern-based insights with 10 hardcoded overall insights
   - Changed selectedInsights state from Pattern[] to string[]
   - Each insight format: "Main text\nWhy? Explanation"
   - Displays as "Insight 1-10" labels instead of confidence scores
   - Insights include mix of successes and missed opportunities

4. Canvas Section Pre-filled Options
   - Added 4 specific selectable insights in Canvas empty state:
     * "Your strongest posts start with uncertainty, not confidence..."
     * "Text-led hooks work better for you than visual openings..."
     * "This idea needed a clearer hook in the first few seconds..."
     * "Posting earlier could have helped this content travel further..."
   - Each card clickable with purple plus icon
   - Clicking adds insight to selectedInsights array
   - Selected insights display as removable cards with X button

5. Generate Ideas Functionality
   - Fixed generateIdeas function to work with string-based insights
   - Changed from accessing i.theme to i.split('\n')[0]
   - Now extracts main text from string format and sends to AI agent
   - Pre-populates draft with first generated idea's hook and concept
   - Navigates to drafts screen instead of removed explore screen
   - Fully functional end-to-end workflow

6. Explore Ideas Section Removal
   - Removed 'explore' from currentScreen type definition
   - Removed 'Explore' navigation item from sidebar
   - Removed renderExplore() conditional rendering from screen content
   - Updated generateIdeas to navigate to 'drafts' instead
   - Kept renderExplore function for potential future inline display

7. Insights Section Removal & Health/Stats Popup Addition
   - Removed 'insights' from currentScreen type definition
   - Removed 'Insights' navigation item from sidebar
   - Removed renderInsights() conditional rendering
   - Created new aesthetic health/stats popup with:
     * Purple gradient design (purple-50 to pink-50)
     * Heart icon in purple gradient circle
     * Health reminder section with 4 wellness tips
     * Quick stats: Ideas Explored (2), Draft Started (1)
     * Motivational quote
     * Two action buttons: "I'll Take a Break" and "Continue Creating"
   - Added "Health & Stats" button in sidebar footer with heart icon
   - Clicking triggers showHealthPopup modal

Files Modified:
