- /app/nextjs-project/app/page.tsx (complete UI updates)

Technical Changes:
==================
- State type change: selectedInsights from Pattern[] to string[]
- New state: showHealthPopup boolean
- Function fix: generateIdeas now uses string.split('\n')[0]
- Navigation workflow: Content Builder → Generate Ideas → Drafts (with pre-populated first idea)
- Removed screen types: 'explore', 'insights'
- New modal: renderHealthStatsPopup()
- Enhanced modal: renderReflectionModal() with weekly performance

